data.description: In need of single level living? This beautifully maintained brick ranch in Fort Allen has so much to offer! This home creates a cozy atmosphere on the main level with 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath, while the spacious lower level provides ample room for your entertaining needs and a full second bath. When the weather is warm, you can enjoy barbecues out by the pool!
